Acceptance: Implement confirmed end-to-end Issue creation, Issue and PR close/reopen, and typed workflow dispatch. Each operation generates a resolved target/action/typed-input preview and fresh confirmation tied to current revisions and authority, executes through the live GitHub boundary, emits a durable redacted receipt, and reconciles its resulting webhook without duplicate visible output. Success, policy rejection, expired or replayed confirmation, changed target, stale state, idempotent retry, provider failure, receipt, and webhook tests prove no unauthorized or duplicate external mutation. Canonical contract: docs/plans/2026-07-12-github-item-room-routing.md.